# AICON in Isaac Lab

Implementation of **"No Plan but Everything Under Control: Robustly Solving Sequential Tasks
with Dynamically Composed Gradient Descent"** (Mengers & Brock, ICRA 2025) inside Isaac Lab.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install in the Isaac Lab python env
cd /run/media/adhitya/Steam1/IsaacLab
./_isaac_sim/python.sh -m pip install -e /run/media/adhitya/Steam1/no_plan_everything_control

# Run Blocks World experiment
./isaaclab.sh -p /run/media/adhitya/Steam1/no_plan_everything_control/scripts/run_blocks_world.py

# Run Drawer Manipulation experiment
./isaaclab.sh -p /run/media/adhitya/Steam1/no_plan_everything_control/scripts/run_drawer_manipulation.py

# Run tests
./_isaac_sim/python.sh -m pytest /run/media/adhitya/Steam1/no_plan_everything_control/tests/ -v
```

