## Structure

```
source/no_plan_everything_control/
├── aicon/           Pure PyTorch AICON kernel (no Isaac Lab imports)
├── envs/
│   ├── blocks_world/          Experiment 1
│   └── drawer_manipulation/   Experiment 2
└── experiments/               High-level experiment drivers
scripts/             Isaac Lab entry-points
baselines/           State-space and belief-space planners for comparison
tools/               Evaluation and plotting utilities
tests/               Unit and integration tests
```
